[[File:Templar_tower.png|right]]The '''Templar Tower''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It increases the Defensive Value of a limited number of Templars by 100%. If there are not enough Templars in the city, City Guards can take their place and gain the same bonus. These towers don't count towards a city's building number limit.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 8

